title: What You Consume, You Become
itunes:title: What You Consume, You Become
description:
What you consume goes much deeper than the food you eat. Do you really pay attention to everything that you goes into your body? In this episode, I am going to talk about everything that you consume, intentionally and unintentionally, and how it makes you into the person you are.
